Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.07,0:00:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痉挛绝顶子宫顶开发 日下部日奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.01,0:00:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.08,0:00:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天气很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.08,0:00:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.02,0:00:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那在这么热的天气里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.09,0:00:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要来进行拍摄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.09,0:00:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.03,0:00:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是今天要开发你的子宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？会不安吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.11,0:00:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是也有不安啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.05,0:00:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉有点···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有想高潮的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.12,0:01:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愿望？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.06,0:01:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有愿望的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很想做i啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.06,0:01:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很期待 因为想试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.00,0:01:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想高潮个不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.07,0:01:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好意外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,参考了你的粉丝的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.01,0:01:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你能再多做点企划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.09,0:01:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此类的意见很多 很意外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,认为你不擅长这些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.09,0:01:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不是不擅长呢 只是没有机会做而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.03,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比方这样的企划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很期待 会变怎样呢 我自己也不知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 那就请交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.04,0:01:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然让你穿成这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.01,0:02:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比泳衣还害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.08,0:02:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是纸内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.09,0:02:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纸胸罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按摩啊 是想请你来试一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才让你穿成这样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有听过子宫颈按摩吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.04,0:02:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.04,0:03:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有想要再变更敏感的女性 有这样烦恼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.04,0:03:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很适合的按摩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女生的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是更能高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敏感度···更高涨的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如你所说 子宫颈是在子宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.13,0:03:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某部分的名称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.00,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对那里刺激的话 会容易更敏感的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.07,0:03:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.07,0:03:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先不管会不会收录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请务必事先试一下有无效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.08,0:03:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后再进行正式拍摄 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这各环节是挺常有的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.02,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挺常有的 这次嘛 因机会难得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.02,0:03:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会放入纪录片要素的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.03,0:03:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘛 也想当作一个拍摄单元的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:03:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若失败的话就不会当成单元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以放轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.04,0:04:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要当成是拍摄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为有老师会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.05,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵从老师的指示就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请放轻松接受按摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.06,0:04:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失礼了 请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.13,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天 请坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.00,0:04:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要塑造出容易敏感的身体 那样没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有所谓的子宫颈快威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.01,0:04:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子宫颈是子宫的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.08,0:04:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经由舒缓子宫 会带来更大快感的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.02,0:04:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是子宫颈高潮 为了那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.09,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以让全身放松 是很重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.09,0:04:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓的子宫颈按摩不是只有子宫颈而是全身的按摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.03,0:05:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了提高效率 有准备了精油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,边舒缓全身的淋巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,边渐渐的舒缓身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.11,0:05:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多指教 很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,容易敏感的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.05,0:05:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敏感本身是什么意思的你知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敏感本身是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.12,0:05:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是说敏感为什么会敏感？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为很爽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 是因为很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,譬如说 手能请伸出来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.06,0:05:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手伸出来 譬如说 这一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会感觉很痒吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会痒痒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若要说为什么敏感的话 这里有神经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后是像这样有触碰的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.01,0:05:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类的身体会有敏感的部位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有重要的血管经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,譬如说这边也是有动脉经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.09,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动脉经过的地方会有很多神经集中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.02,0:06:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说要保护那边才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经由刺激那些部位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类才会有痛的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓性的快感又是另一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是要刺激有很多神经的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.11,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那会很爽快的 大脑中枢要起变化才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是所谓的性高潮的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.12,0:06:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓女人内部的中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那叫什么？意象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意象？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.06,0:06:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 那很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.13,0:06:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那赶紧的 我想来舒缓身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是要用精油的按摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以请你脱掉衣服吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那请面向前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身体很僵硬的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.11,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会无法有威觉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,硬梆梆的身体就算被摸的 也很难传达到高潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有这种感觉吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.05,0:07:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有 好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.12,0:07:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胸部大的话 这边容易僵硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 肩膀应该很僵硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要渐渐的往胸口这边舒缓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.07,0:08:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手会发抖的这件事本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是身体很紧张的表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.01,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以为了舒缓那样子 请大大的深呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.09,0:08:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 是的 请记在心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要停止呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.09,0:08:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢地用鼻子吸气 从嘴吐气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从嘴吐气的感觉 像是上牙床用力的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.04,0:08:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.05,0:08:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.05,0:08:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为是不会突然就舒缓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.12,0:08:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请尽可能用呼吸放松 没关系哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手举高吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.01,0:09:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后维持着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.08,0:09:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请挺胸的状态下维持着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.02,0:09:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.03,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 可以了 边吐气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要边扭动哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扭动？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.11,0:09:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 吸气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.04,0:09:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 慢慢吐气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.12,0:09:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 再吸一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 另一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.13,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 回来 好 放下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.01,0:10:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那请躺下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,头朝这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.02,0:10:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.05,0:10:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒 有舒缓的威觉、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.07,0:11:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要伸展这边肩膀的筋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.00,0:11:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请手往前伸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腰请抬起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手请撑在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.02,0:11:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腰抬起来手肘撑着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后要伸展肩膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.09,0:11:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,边吐气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 先用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.11,0:11:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那请吸气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.11,0:12:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,边吐气 边伸展身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.05,0:12:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.05,0:12:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再回来一次 然后再一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.07,0:12:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,膝盖稍微打开点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后往后伸展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再来一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.02,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会痛吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变温暖了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.03,0:12:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后接着转过来正面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要来舒缓淋巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.06,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手举高吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.00,0:13:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.04,0:14:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子会痛吗这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.04,0:14:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事？好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.04,0:14:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这子宫上面的部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.05,0:14:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢来舒缓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.07,0:14:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要开始抹精油了 失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.04,0:15:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很紧张啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.11,0:15:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请大大的深呼吸 放轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.05,0:15:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样的话 身体温暖的咸觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.12,0:15:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会更能感受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.07,0:15:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,膝盖弯起来 要来舒缓股关节哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.03,0:16:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鼠蹊部这边也要舒缓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.04,0:16:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脚这边的淋巴跟上半身有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.04,0:16:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要舒缓才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.04,0:16:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候身体会有温暖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.05,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会更容易高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.12,0:16:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有感觉到酥麻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来才要开始哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.06,0:16:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.10,0:17:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那刚说过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.04,0:17:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来确认子宫颈的部位哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.01,0:18:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.00,0:19:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很怪的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.07,0:19:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很怪的感觉？放轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.07,0:19:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.02,0:19:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要来给予点振动哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.09,0:20:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.04,0:20:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.12,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.00,0:21:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.08,0:21:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.10,0:21:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再来多舒缓点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.12,0:22:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚的振动还残留着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.12,0:22:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚是振动刺激身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.06,0:22:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次对内侧的子宫颈直接给予刺激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.07,0:22:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.03,0:22:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是初期的状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.10,0:22:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还能更有感觉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.06,0:23:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.08,0:23:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉没问题吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.02,0:23:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很热啊身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.05,0:24:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.08,0:24:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？按摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.02,0:24:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.02,0:24:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害 舒缓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.03,0:25:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部 好厉害 子宫颈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.03,0:25:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.11,0:25:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.04,0:25:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想已经很完美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.05,0:25:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 好害羞 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.05,0:25:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以开拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.12,0:25:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.12,0:25:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很期待？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.06,0:26:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？加奈酱 刚刚的性感开发单元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.00,0:26:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.00,0:26:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被按这边 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.07,0:26:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被按到子宫高潮了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.01,0:26:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 这里是子宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.08,0:27:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子宫附近啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.08,0:27:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身体怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:07.09,0:27:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该说是塑形了呢 已经完成了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.09,0:27:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.10,0:27:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身体也变很热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.10,0:27:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在眼睛有点迷濛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.10,0:27:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.10,0:27:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那这单元是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.04,0:27:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子宫口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.05,0:27:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用肉棒抽插的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.05,0:27:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.12,0:27:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道子宫口吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.12,0:27:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子宫口？子宫的···入口？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:43.12,0:27:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 刚刚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:44.06,0:27:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.13,0:27:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚也有按过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.06,0:27:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用肉棒抽插的话 会高潮吧的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.00,0:27:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要用这支肉棒做做看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.01,0:28:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能请你摸一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:06.08,0:28:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一脸很开心的表情好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.08,0:28:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉很大的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.09,0:28:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也摸摸里面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.10,0:28:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.10,0:28:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:27.04,0:28:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得很大 好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:34.11,0:28:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那这个靠近点看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:38.11,0:28:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠近看？好近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:45.05,0:28:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.06,0:28:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是这个的话 子宫口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:56.00,0:28:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肉棒的前端有可能能顶到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.07,0:29:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.00,0:29:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个可能能让子宫很爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:05.07,0:29:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.01,0:29:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在摸着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.02,0:29:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那因为身体已经舒缓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:18.02,0:29:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来开始做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:41.11,0:29:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銮相当温暖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:44.05,0:29:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变很热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.08,0:30:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 若这样做的话会变怎样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:42.10,0:30:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在啊 这大肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.04,0:30:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在想着插到子宫口的事情对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.05,0:30:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.13,0:32:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么在摸着啊？现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.06,0:32:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉很爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.00,0:32:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己也想多爽点啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.07,0:32:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:28.08,0:32:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过还有想要我摸的地方吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.02,0:32:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.09,0:32:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:42.09,0:32:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说这里可能听不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:46.09,0:32:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.03,0:32:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要你摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.02,0:33:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.08,0:33:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己很爽的地方 现在在碰着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:18.05,0:34:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.09,0:34:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腰在扭动着啊 从刚开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.09,0:34:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很爽 所以会扭动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:01.03,0:35:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想更爽点吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:04.10,0:35:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.10,0:35:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还只是摸子宫口而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:25.05,0:35:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.01,0:35:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.01,0:35:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有感觉了？那只有外面就好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.01,0:35:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 里面也想要爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:22.04,0:36:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在到这边对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.05,0:36:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:27.12,0:36:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有碰到子宫口吗？现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.05,0:36:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.06,0:36:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？现在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.13,0:36:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很怪的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.08,0:37:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.09,0:37:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以再多玩弄点子宫口吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.03,0:37:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请尽情玩弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.12,0:37:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:44.13,0:37:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:53.07,0:37:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.01,0:38:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去了
